               ] Nothing ſo inimical to love as fear and neceſſity. When all jealouſies of any ſiniſter ends are blown away, then exhortations and counſels go down comfortably. When perſons are convinced and ſatisfied that in all our Applications we ſtudy their benefit and profit, this opens an effectual door to all the means that we ſhall uſe.Rom. 1.11. Thus the Apoſtle accoaſts the Romans, I long to ſee you, that I may impart unto you ſome ſpiritual gift. Thus he facilitates his way to the Philippians.
