               ] wee do even naturally reſpect and reverence ſuch as bring that which appears profitable to us;Simplicius in Epictet. c. 38. p. 217. Ed Salm. eſpecially when Superiors carry themſelves with courteouſneſs and kindneſs. For moſt men delight to be honoured and eſteemed by them that are above them [
